ygData.messageBody:
Hmm the last time I tried to camp in my Work Zone I was warned for
disruption...

GM TheBoss says "This is a verbal warning, Kevin, don't do that again".

EEK!!!
HEHEHE

Lyrnia Jongleur
Bard of Norrath
